1820
01:26:32,890 --> 01:26:35,280
Did you want to be a
 musician when you were a kid?

1821
01:26:35,280 --> 01:26:39,230
My grandmother took charge of
 what I wanted when I was a kid.

1822
01:26:39,230 --> 01:26:40,260
What did she want?

1823
01:26:40,260 --> 01:26:43,010
For me to finish high school.

1824
01:26:43,010 --> 01:26:44,840
She had her hand on
 my back for 10 years.

1825
01:26:44,840 --> 01:26:45,820
