1877
01:28:55,080 --> 01:28:56,450
Are they excited?

1878
01:28:56,450 --> 01:28:57,150
And how.

1879
01:28:57,150 --> 01:28:58,380
They couldn't wait
 to get to Florida

1880
01:28:58,380 --> 01:29:01,110
so they can go to Disney World.

1881
01:29:01,110 --> 01:29:03,780
El, you've been on
 the shuttle before.

1882
01:29:03,780 --> 01:29:06,030
Do you think taking
 civilians up,

1883
01:29:06,030 --> 01:29:10,860
any civilians, teachers,
 politicians, is a good idea?

1884
01:29:10,860 --> 01:29:13,050
I personally don't
 feel that we should

1885
01:29:13,050 --> 01:29:15,670
