1886
01:29:15,670 --> 01:29:17,790
There's still a lot of
 questions about the shuttle.

1887
01:29:17,790 --> 01:29:19,500
We should make sure
 it's as safe as possible

1888
01:29:19,500 --> 01:29:22,500
before we start flying
 too many civilians.

1889
01:29:22,500 --> 01:29:24,330
On the other hand,
 I wouldn't mind

1890
01:29:24,330 --> 01:29:27,030
a malfunction or two once
 the Challenger reaches orbit.

1891
01:29:27,030 --> 01:29:29,460
I spent a lot of time,
 hours, underwater training

1892
01:29:29,460 --> 01:29:32,850
