 and practicing a lot.

1903
01:29:58,030 --> 01:29:58,870
That's how we train.

1904
01:29:58,870 --> 01:30:00,640
We practice a lot.

1905
01:30:00,640 --> 01:30:03,100
Do you practice so much that
 when you actually get there,

1906
01:30:03,100 --> 01:30:05,110
it's an anticlimax.

