Christa is a
 wonderful teacher,

1913
01:30:17,710 --> 01:30:19,930
but we haven't
 talked about that.

1914
01:30:19,930 --> 01:30:21,840
You ought to ask
 her what she thinks.

1915
01:30:21,840 --> 01:30:25,240
Christa, are you excited yet?

1916
01:30:25,240 --> 01:30:27,040
Well, when this
 started, I didn't

1917
01:30:27,040 --> 01:30:28,680
think I could get
 any more excited,

1918
01:30:28,680 --> 01:30:31,540
