 wreck by the time we launch.

1920
01:30:34,660 --> 01:30:36,610
Didn't your family
 come down for a visit?

1921
01:30:36,610 --> 01:30:38,140
Yes, they did.

1922
01:30:38,140 --> 01:30:39,040
NASA was wonderful.

1923
01:30:39,040 --> 01:30:41,380
They took them on a tour
 of the whole Space Center.

1924
01:30:41,380 --> 01:30:43,590
What part did they like best?

1925
01:30:43,590 --> 01:30:46,680
Well, I asked my daughter
 Caroline what she enjoyed most,

1926
01:30:46,680 --> 01:30:49,980
she said the tuna sandwich.

1927
01:30:49,980 --> 01:30:53,250
Christa, do you have any
 concerns about the trip?

1928
01:30:53,250 --> 01:30:54,900
Are you worried?

1929
01:30:54,900 --> 01:30:57,390
Are you afraid?

1930
01:30:57,390 --> 01:31:00,480
Well, I can honestly
 say that I'm not .

1931
01:31:00,480 --> 01:31:03,130
Maybe I will be when I
 walk across that catwalk,

1932
01:31:03,130 --> 01:31:07,050
but right now there's
 so much to do.

1933
01:31:07,050 --> 01:31:11,370
This crew has made me feel
 that I'm a part of them.

1934
01:31:11,370 --> 01:31:13,200
There's no group of
 people that I'd rather

1935
01:31:13,200 --> 01:31:15,810
be sharing this adventure
 with, no group of people

1936
01:31:15,810 --> 01:31:17,970
