1939
01:31:21,420 --> 01:31:25,070
Has Christa really
 become part of the crew?

1940
01:31:25,070 --> 01:31:26,880
Well, thinking anybody
 who hasn't been trained

1941
01:31:26,880 --> 01:31:30,510
