1955
01:32:10,860 --> 01:32:11,700
Yes.

1956
01:32:11,700 --> 01:32:14,490
What do you tell them?

1957
01:32:14,490 --> 01:32:16,630
Well, that's not really the
 province of today's questions,

1958
01:32:16,630 --> 01:32:17,330
is it?

1959
01:32:17,330 --> 01:32:19,150
Why don't you ask me
 questions about laser physics

1960
01:32:19,150 --> 01:32:20,240
or Halley's comet?

1961
01:32:20,240 --> 01:32:24,770
It's an aspect of you
 that I'd like to know about.

1962
01:32:24,770 --> 01:32:28,520
All right, I tell them it
 doesn't matter who you are,

1963
01:32:28,520 --> 01:32:31,970
where you come from, or
 how much money you have,

1964
01:32:31,970 --> 01:32:33,830
if you want to reach
 a goal badly enough

1965
01:32:33,830 --> 01:32:38,560
and you're willing to
 work hard to get it,

1966
01:32:38,560 --> 01:32:39,790
you can be what you want to be.

1967
01:32:42,530 --> 01:32:44,410
How does it feel
 to finally be getting

1968
01:32:44,410 --> 01:32:46,330
a chance to fly in the shuttle?

1969
01:32:46,330 --> 01:32:47,350
All right.

1970
01:32:47,350 --> 01:32:50,030
Well, basically, fantastic.

1971
01:32:50,030 --> 01:32:51,850
